{"tid":1909794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看看什麼是億萬蝗蟲大軍！","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T05:25:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44ab8976f1c0ef3bd2d5b84bc01a306d60ec9ca9","tid":1909794,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"3月3日，有網友發一段視頻並附文說，給你看看啥叫蝗災！十萬隻鴨子恐怕難擋其攻勢，保不齊被蝗蟲給吃了！<br />\n<br />\n    <em>给你看看啥叫蝗灾！<br />\n<br />\n    十万只鸭子恐怕难挡其攻势，保不齐被蝗虫给吃了！? <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/KnHbxAoRlf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FKnHbxAoRlf&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=c855ceca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/KnHbxAoRlf</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; 深眸 (@deepeyes2018) March 2, 2020</em><br />\n<br />\n視頻中無數蝗蟲在空中飛行，氣勢非常駭人。網友們紛紛熱議：<br />\n<br />\n「太可怕了！」<br />\n「真是恐怖！」<br />\n「蝗軍來勢洶洶呀！」<br />\n「恐怖：飛蝗過處、寸草不留！」<br />\n「再多100倍鴨子可能差不多！」<br />\n<br />\n「鳥去哪了？」<br />\n「皇蟲這氣勢，鳥也不傻。」<br />\n「蝗蟲會把動物身上的毛髮都啃光的。恐怖！」<br />\n「遮天蔽日，有颱風，或火災，水災，也許能消滅了&hellip;&hellip;.」<br />\n也有人嘲諷：「放心，共匪已研發殺蝗蟲的新冠狀病毒！」<br />\n<br />\n幾日前，媒體報導浙江十萬隻鴨子出征巴基斯坦滅蝗的消息，幾小時後當局迅即出面闢謠。中國蝗災防治組說，巴基斯坦並不適合以鴨子捕食蝗蟲的方法來滅蝗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/03/04/a102791484.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F03%2F04%2Fa102791484.html&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=8891fc32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/03/04/a102791484.html</a>"},{"pid":"f0d4b8e27502a507d6acda3479f72c58f85af88a","tid":1909794,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a2fe0848f33c898e0a3b86c8190b38abe42e2d45","tid":1909794,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1234624346691256322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1234624346691256322&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=a74d53e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1234624346691256322&h=b4d9c525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1234624346691256322</a>"},{"pid":"e867e4628df80728489ea3d947aa041f5fdad698","tid":1909794,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"原來鴨 識飛㗎？？"}]}